type: Tutorial Step - Congrats and Thank You!

definition.text: This is awesome! You just arrived and are already contributing to the project! We are grateful for your first contribution!

paragraphs.text: If everything went well with your authentication, you should be seeing the Contribution Done message!
Ok my friend, we're going to start wraping this up!
Before I let you go, I'll give you a few pointers as to what is the best way forwards with learning Superalgos, how to engage with the community, and how to make a second valuable contribution!
